===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Aredale had a population of 62 people, with 32 households and 21 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A02620&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A02620&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 61.9 inhabitants per square mile (23.9/km<sup>2</sup>), and there were 36 housing units at an average density of 35.9 per square mile (13.9/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref>{{cite web |title=2020 Census |url=https://www.census.gov/programs-surveys/decennial-census/decade/2020/2020-census-main.html |publisher=United States Census Bureau}}</ref>

All residents lived in rural areas. There were 36 housing units, of which 11.1% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A02620&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 32 households, of which 40.6% had children under the age of 18 living with them. Of all households, 40.6% were married-couple households, 12.5% were cohabiting-couple households, 37.5% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present, and 9.4% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present. In total, 34.4% of households were non-families, 21.9% were made up of individuals, and 15.7% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age was 50.0 years. 21.0% of residents were under the age of 18 and 37.1% were 65 years of age or older. By broader age brackets, 1.6% of residents were between 20 and 24, 21.0% were from 25 to 44, and 17.7% were from 45 to 64. For every 100 females, there were 113.8 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 113.0 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/><ref name="Census2020PL"/>

